The year's Classic Homes and Auto Expo 2017 partnered with Commercial Bank of Africa (CBA), the largest privately owned bank in Kenya.Home owners, future home owners and auto mobile enthusiasts flocked Kenyatta International Conference center for the three-day expo.The expo is an annual event that has been running since 2013 and this year's was the biggest providing a platform for exhibitors who deal with matters home and cars to showcase their different products.From land, building materials, already built homes, furnishings, insurance companies and cars.